## [Unreleased] - 2021-09-20

### Added
- Added All notification api
- Added Push notification in case of checkin,checkout,login
- Added FCM api script
- Added FCM Topic model for topics
- Addede Mobikul Attendance Messages model to store the messages of certain employee
- Added the FCM for the notification
- Added the FCM Topic View
- Added the Mobikul Attendance Messages View

### Changed
- Some change in ir_http file for notification images 
- Change res_user file and add the support to remove device in case of reset password from email link
- Change csv file for new model access 


### Fixed
- Fix all API's naming issue and model naming issue from attendence to attendance

